comments: Lowry (TOR) is moving slightly toward Green (PHI) when some contact occurs with Green's body/right arm along the sideline, and the contact is marginal.
Anunoby (TOR) reaches in and makes contact across Green's (PHI) right arm at the end of the drive, causing Green to lose control of the ball.
Harris (PHI) is turning slightly as he establishes verticality and absorbs the body contact made with VanVleet (TOR) during his shot attempt near the rim.
Curry (PHI) makes incidental contact with Anunoby's (TOR) right arm after making clean contact with the ball.

Green (PHI) swipes down and makes contact across Siakam's (TOR) right wrist, causing Siakam to lose control of the ball after his gather. After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined Siakam touched the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Embiid (PHI) firms up in his screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.

VanVleet (TOR) has his arm extended forward as the hand-off takes place and some contact occurs with Curry's (PHI) left arm as Curry bobbles the ball, which he gains full control of momentarily after.
Green (PHI) and Anunoby (TOR) engage and disengage with one another as the pick expires.
Lowry's (TOR) hand naturally comes forward as he shifts his momentum and marginal contact occurs with Harris' (PHI) backside as he releases.
Embiid (PHI) and Baynes (TOR) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another during rebounding.
Siakam (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with Simmons (PHI) at the end of the drive.
VanVleet (TOR) attempts to commit the take foul on Harris (PHI) and the contact is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) commits the take foul on Harris (PHI).
Baynes (TOR) begins rolling out of his screening position and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs with Thybulle (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) is moving in a straight line toward the basket when Lowry (TOR) veers into him and initiates the marginal body contact after his gather.
Lowry (TOR) is moving slightly forward when marginal body contact occurs with Harris (PHI) along the baseline.
Harris (PHI) keeps his feet in-bounds as he dribbles along the baseline in the backcourt.
Lowry (TOR) is moving alongside Harris (PHI) and marginal arm contact occurs prior to Harris losing control of the ball on his own.
PHI inbounds the ball at 21.2 and the timeout is awarded at 14.4.
Thomas (TOR) and Harris (PHI) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
VanVleet (TOR) extends his arm forward and incidental contact occurs with Curry (PHI) as VanVleet deflects the inbound pass.
Curry (PHI) drops the ball in-bounds before his momentum carries him out of bounds, and he re-establishes himself in bounds before making further contact with the ball.
Lowry (TOR) commits the take foul on Curry (PHI).
Green (PHI) makes legal hand-on-ball contact with Baynes (TOR) during his upward shooting motion.
